text: Danny Woodhead (born January 25, 1985 in North Platte, Nebraska) is an American football running back for the New England Patriots of the National Football League (NFL). Woodhead made his NFL debut with the New York Jets in 2008 and was signed by the New England Patriots on September 18, 2010. ==Other websites== * Danny Woodhead at nfl.com Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:New England Patriots players Category:American football running backs Category:Sportspeople from Nebraska Category:People from North Platte, Nebraska
